oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Innovations in Ruminant Nutrition
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Olentine, Charles
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: ruminant Nutrition
biochemistry
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Even though I am not a practicing veterinarian I would like to thank you for the opportunity to speak concerning nutrition. I think we have moved away from the concept of a nutritionist being the feed and weigh and the feeds and feeding type. We are in an era now where nutrition is really biochemistry.
